{"id":"api-bruno-collection-prerequest","type":"api_behavior","fact":"Bruno CLI (@usebruno/cli) supports script:pre-request in collection.bru under recursive (-r) runs — the hook fires before every request. Node built-ins plus 'axios' are available in the sandbox via require().","recommendation":"Use collection.bru's script:pre-request for idempotent auth bootstrap (check if accessToken is empty → POST /api/auth/login → bru.setVar). Guard with a _authBootstrapFailed flag to prevent rate-limit amplification on repeated login failures. Fallback if this ever breaks: a seq-0 _auth-bootstrap/login.bru folder.","confidence":"high","provenance":[{"source":"agent","reference":"Issue #28 WU-002 spike","date":"2026-04-13"}],"tags":["bruno","collection","pre-request","auth","axios"],"affectedFiles":["bruno/collection.bru"],"affectedServices":[],"createdAt":"2026-04-13T00:00:00Z","updatedAt":"2026-04-13T00:00:00Z","usageCount":0,"helpfulCount":0,"outdatedReports":0}
